        "content": "<p>I want to do a poc for using wasi http - is this avwailable in any platform?<br>\nit doesn't have to be production ready</p>",
        "id": 405362825,
        "sender_full_name": "Gregor Zeitlinger",
        "timestamp": 1701437065
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>wasmtime has a subcommand that supports it out of the box: <code>wasmtime serve</code>.</p>\n<p>If you're looking for hosting environments, I know that Cosmonic has support, but would have to defer to <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"421591\">@Bailey Hayes</span> for details, and my employer Fermyon has a Wasmtime based runtime called <a href=\"https://developer.fermyon.com/spin/index\">Spin</a> that runs wasi-http in production</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://developer.fermyon.com/spin/index\" style=\"background-image: url(https\\:\\/\\/uploads\\.zulipusercontent\\.net\\/35d6be246a07a5e6039e6c42a1f9c7e2eb03ea3c\\/68747470733a2f2f646576656c6f7065722e6665726d796f6e2e636f6d2f7374617469632f696d6167652f747769747465725f636172645f73756d6d6172792e706e67)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://developer.fermyon.com/spin/index\" title=\"Introducing Spin\">Introducing Spin</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">\nA checklist app that persists data in a key value store\n</div></div></div>",
        "id": 405372599,
        "sender_full_name": "Till Schneidereit",
        "timestamp": 1701439995
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>And if you're looking for guest examples, here are a few:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sunfishcode/hello-wasi-http\">https://github.com/sunfishcode/hello-wasi-http</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Mossaka/hello-wasi-http-go\">https://github.com/Mossaka/hello-wasi-http-go</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/componentize-py/tree/main/examples/http\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/componentize-py/tree/main/examples/http</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/sunfishcode/hello-wasi-http\" style=\"background-image: url(https\\:\\/\\/uploads\\.zulipusercontent\\.net\\/44e27f1a4fde41414af0959352cab2ee77d38401\\/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f323738346533623634353630316333316362306633656136383736643134656533616132346134376436303835666636343465626264633833366139653161312f73756e66697368636f64652f68656c6c6f2d776173692d68747470)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sunfishcode/hello-wasi-http\" title=\"GitHub - sunfishcode/hello-wasi-http\">GitHub - sunfishcode/hello-wasi-http</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">Contribute to sunfishcode/hello-wasi-http development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></div></div><div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/Mossaka/hello-wasi-http-go\" style=\"background-image: url(https\\:\\/\\/uploads\\.zulipusercontent\\.net\\/689096bb15475718dc448982181952ceb841cd4b\\/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f653461393732393163386363346538666139656666363833623234303362306163636236666537616230373166653230323063343632313561363236326266392f4d6f7373616b612f68656c6c6f2d776173692d687474702d676f)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Mossaka/hello-wasi-http-go\